 nflation pressure before it reaches consumers.\n\n• Frequency: Monthly
  in the US. Quarterly in Australia.\n\n• Notes: PPI is usually less ma
 rket-moving than CPI\, but it can still matter when inflation is the mai
 n macro theme.\n\n• Acronyms: PPI = Producer Price Index.\n\nOfficial 
